# Veliora.AI — Canonical Architectural Documentation (Part 1)

## System Overview & Core Backend

> **Document Scope:** This is Part 1 of 3 of the exhaustive architectural reference for the Veliora.AI dual-architecture ecosystem. It covers the system overview, core backend orchestration, configuration, authentication, chat pipeline, voice infrastructure, and LLM engine.

---

## 1. Dual-Architecture Overview

Veliora.AI is a **dual-architecture ecosystem** comprising two independently deployable but interconnected systems:

### Architecture A: AI Persona Orchestration (Port 8000)
- **Framework:** FastAPI (Python 3.11+, ASGI via Uvicorn)
- **Purpose:** Customizable AI companion ecosystem with persona-driven conversational intelligence
- **AI Stack:** Gemini 2.0 Flash (LLM), RoBERTa GoEmotions (text emotion), HuBERT SUPERB-ER (speech emotion), Deepgram Nova-2 (STT), Cartesia Sonic (TTS)
- **Data Layer:** Redis Stack (RediSearch + HNSW vectors) for active state; Supabase PostgreSQL for persistence
- **Async Pipeline:** RabbitMQ (durable queues) for memory extraction and message logging

### Architecture B: Real-Time Human Communication — "Familia" (Port 8001)
- **Framework:** FastAPI (separate app instance)
- **Purpose:** Cross-cultural human connection platform with verified identities, translated messaging, bonding contests, and family rooms
- **Translation:** Google Cloud Translation API v2 + Gemini 2.0 Flash for cultural context/idiom detection
- **Data Layer:** Supabase PostgreSQL exclusively (all tables suffixed `_realtime`)
- **Real-Time:** WebSocket `ConnectionManager` for live chat, typing indicators, read receipts

### Shared Infrastructure
| Component | Used By |
|-----------|---------|
| Supabase PostgreSQL | Both (separate table namespaces) |
| Deepgram STT | Both (voice calls + voice verification) |
| Cartesia TTS | Both (voice responses + voice messages) |
| `.env` credentials | Shared root `.env` file |

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    VELIORA.AI ECOSYSTEM                         │
│                                                                 │
│  ┌──────────────────────┐    ┌──────────────────────────────┐  │
│  │  AI Persona Backend  │    │  Familia Realtime Backend    │  │
│  │  (FastAPI :8000)     │    │  (FastAPI :8001)             │  │
│  │                      │    │                              │  │
│  │  • Chat API          │    │  • Chat + Translation        │  │
│  │  • Voice WebSocket   │    │  • Friends + Matching        │  │
│  │  • Games Engine      │    │  • Contests + Games          │  │
│  │  • Emotion Pipeline  │    │  • Family Rooms              │  │
│  │  • Memory System     │    │  • Verification              │  │
│  │  • Selfie Gen        │    │  • Safety + Moderation       │  │
│  │  • Diary CRON        │    │  • XP + Leaderboards         │  │
│  └──────────┬───────────┘    └──────────────┬───────────────┘  │
│             │                                │                  │
│  ┌──────────▼────────────────────────────────▼───────────────┐  │
│  │              SHARED INFRASTRUCTURE                        │  │
│  │  Supabase (PostgreSQL + Storage + Auth)                   │  │
│  │  Redis Stack (HNSW Vector Search, Caching)                │  │
│  │  RabbitMQ (Async Memory/Message Queues)                   │  │
