## 7. LLM Engine — `services/llm_engine.py` (640 lines)

**File:** [llm_engine.py](file:///Users/likhith./Veliora.AI_backend./services/llm_engine.py)

Central gateway for all Gemini 2.0 Flash interactions. Uses `google.genai.Client`.

### 7.1 Core Functions

| Function | Purpose | Input | Output |
|----------|---------|-------|--------|
| `generate_chat_response()` | Main chat completion | system_prompt, context, user_msg, memories | str (bot response) |
| `generate_embedding()` | Text→Vector embedding | text string | List[float] (768-dim) |
| `describe_image()` | Multimodal image description | base64 image, bot_id, language | str (description) |
| `generate_scene_description()` | Selfie scene from chat context | bot_id, context list | str (scene prompt) |
| `summarize_url_content()` | URL content summarization | content text, bot_id | str (summary) |
| `generate_text_meme()` | Persona-voiced meme | bot_id, topic, language | str (meme text) |
| `generate_diary_entry()` | Nightly diary generation | bot_id, user_name, daily_summary | str (diary entry) |
| `analyze_sentiment_for_dashboard()` | Dashboard insight generation | emotion_data | dict (narrative, predictions) |
| `generate_dashboard_insights()` | AI-powered dashboard insights | telemetry summary | dict (narrative, prediction, suggestions) |

### 7.2 Prompt Construction
All functions inject persona context via `bot_prompt.py` templates. The `generate_chat_response()` function constructs a rich prompt:
```
[System Prompt (persona definition)]
[Semantic Memories: "You remember: ..."]
[RFM Memories: "Important context: ..."]
[Emotion State: "User's current emotional state: ..."]
[Chat Context: last N messages]
[User Message]
```

### 7.3 Error Handling & Retry
All Gemini calls are wrapped in try/except with:
- Automatic retry on `429 Resource Exhausted` (rate limit)
- Fallback to `GOOGLE_API_KEY_2` on persistent failures
- Graceful degradation returning empty strings/defaults on total failure
